    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.46cm; line-height: 100%;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Владимир Ильич Садыков</span></p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 100%;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="en-US">М.П.</span></span></p>